{"lemma":"قِرْبَةٌ","slug":"قِرْبَةٌ","root":"ق.ر.ب","root_slug":"ق-ر-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ر-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"قِرْبَةٌ","root":"قرب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35396"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"water container"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bladder"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bagpipe"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"kinship"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"See جِرَاب (jirāb)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35396","headword_ar":"قِرْبَةٌ","root":"qrb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A kind of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siqaA='","text_ar":"سِقَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skin"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, * O, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used for water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waTob","text_ar":"وَطْب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skin"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is used for milk,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sometimes for water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is sewed on one side:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) [the modern"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qirobap","text_ar":"قِرْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is seldom, if ever, used for anything but water, is (if I may judge from my own observations and the accounts of others) always made of the skin of a goat about one year old or upwards: it consists of nearly the whole skin; only the skin of the head, 